Hmm zm map

This is my first time making zm map, very fun to make and very simple compared to ze mapping experience.

The reason i made zm map is because there is mapping contest on nide.gg server.

This map has same theme as ze_surf_cherry_blossom !! which is also i made them.

MAP OVERVIEW


PIANO


Yep, this map has piano in it. You can play it by pressing E on each of them. If you confused how to enter it, you can enter it by crouching.  Located at the outdoor room.

RADIO


Let you play random songs!!. There is total 12 songs you can play by pressing E. Located at indoor room.

RANDOM TELEPORTER


So this triangle looking thing is a random teleporter. They can be found all around the map, giving you advantage to running all around the map. The destination is random, so be carefull to use them!!

TELEPORT DESTINATION


And this is cylinder looking thing is the destination of random teleporter. Located all around the map.

All song list can be found inside the map.
So that's all of it, and thank you for reading until this far!!
